maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: This is \c[3]So'najiz Temple\c[0]. One of the temples in Gaia's Garden.
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: C'est le \c[3]\v[area.wave-dng.name]\c[0]. Un des temples dans le \v[area.jungle.name].

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: Are you sure you want to enter the dungeon already, Lea?
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: Est-ce que tu es sûre de déjà vouloir entrer dans le donjon, Lea ?

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: Shouldn't you meet up with \c[3]C'tron\c[0] first?
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: Est-ce que tu devais pas rencontrer \c[3]C'tron\c[0] avant ?

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: Come on, Lea. No more dungeon running today.
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: Aller, Lea. Plus de course au donjon pour aujourd'hui.

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: There is still another day tomorrow, right?
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: On a toujours le temps de faire ça demain, non ?

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: Here we go...\. Let the race continue!!
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: Et...\. la course continue !!

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: Uhm...\. we already started the race of the \c[3]Zir'vitar Temple\c[0].
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: Euh...\. On a déjà commencé la course sur le \c[3]\v[area.shock-dng.name]\c[0].

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: I mean we can just put that race on the hold and run the \c[3]So'najiz Temple\c[0] instead.
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: Je veux dire, on pourrait mettre cette course en pause et courir le \c[3]\v[area.wave-dng.name]\c[0] à la place.

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: It's your call!
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: C'est ton choix !

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: You want to start the race of the So'najiz Temple?
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: Tu veux démarrer la course au \v[area.wave-dng.name] ?

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: Hm... Looking at your stats and level, do you really think that you're prepared, Lea?
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: Euh... en regardant tes stats et ton niveau, tu penses vraiment que tu es prête, Lea ?

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: True... I heard your average stats should be somewhat above \c[3]180\c[0].
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: C'est vrai... J'ai cru comprendre que la moyenne de tes stats devrait être au-dessus de \c[3]180\c[0].

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: We can look for better equipment at Basin Keep first, if you want.
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: On peut retourner au \v[area.jungle-city.name] pour chercher du meilleur équipement, si tu veux.

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: Anyway it's your call!
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: En tout cas, c'est comme tu veux !

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: I think we're all well prepared, non?
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: Je pense qu'on est tous bien préparés, non ?

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: Ready to start the race of the So'najiz Temple?
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: Prêt pour démarrer la course au \v[area.wave-dng.name] ?

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: [nods]
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: [acquiesce]

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: Okey-dokey!
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: Dacodac !

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: Everybody get ready!
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: À vos marques tout le monde !

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: [shakes head]
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: [secoue la tête]

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: D'accord, just don't let us wait for too long~
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: D'accord, mais ne nous fais pas attendre trop longtemps~

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: [yes]
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: [oui]

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: [no]
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: [non]

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: Hey Lea, we should call C'tron before entering the Temple.
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: Hé, Lea, on devrait appeler C'tron avant d'entrer dans le temple.

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: Don't forget about our race, non?
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: Tu n'as pas oublié pour notre course, non ?

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: Lea, what about Emilie? We wanted to race the dungeon together, right?
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: Lea, et pour Emilie ? On voulait faire la course au donjon ensemble, non ?

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: Lea, what about that dungeon race? You were planning to enter the dungeon together with Emilie and C'tron, right?
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: Lea, tu as pensé à la course ? Tu voulais entrer dans le donjon avec Emilie et C'tron, correct ?

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: Standing in front of \c[3]So'najiz Temple\c[0]!
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: Est-ce qu'il faut que je le présente ? Le \c[3]\v[area.wave-dng.name]\c[0] !

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: So nice~
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: Trop cool~

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: Hey Tronny...\. Tronny...\. you see this?
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: Hé, Tronny...\. Tronny...\. tu as vu ?

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: It's in the middle of a \c[3]lake\c[0].
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: Le temple est au milieu d'un \c[3]lac\c[0].

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: Yes...\. it is.\. What about it?
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: Oui...\. il l'est.\. Pourquoi ?

maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.orig: Oh...\. nothing.
maps/jungle/dng/wave-exterior.json/entit.text: Oh...\. rien.
